The rates of mortality in Tables 1 - 84 of this Appendix are per 1,000 lives. Tables for both Age Nearest Birthday (ANB) and Age Last Birthday (ALB) have been provided for Composite, Nonsmoker, and Smoker based on Select and Ultimate (S&U) and Ultimate Only (Ult).
